<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200928/c896ae95a7f9442e96a0d8bacc4663f1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《翁松禅相国大字法帖》墨拓 民国旧印本</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200928/d42b95c5f8c34238a4d01d4548300f61.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
